            <h2 class="section-title">You Suspect Mold. You're Not Alone.</h2>
            <p class="section-description">
              That feeling of doubt when you see a strange spot or smell a musty odor is common. This guide is for the "Responsible Homeowner" who wants to investigate properly before spending thousands. We'll explore what DIY mold kits can—and can't—do for you.
            </p>
          </div>

